      "brand_mission_title": "Our Mission",
      "brand_mission_desc": "With a craftsman's heart, we give wood a second life. We don't just make furniture; we create life-long companions. We blend traditional techniques with modern design to bring warmth and uniqueness to every home.",
      "brand_story_title": "Our Story",
      "brand_story_desc": "\"We never believe in wood as it is.\" At CANG WOOD, every fiber twist is a question. We doubt the existing proportions, doubt the function of course, and doubt whether the so-called \"perfection\" is just a banal cover-up. This kind of doubt is our highest respect for materials. We converge this uneasiness into the absolute realm of 1mm. In that error of less than a millimeter, it is the most serious waiting of the unorthodox soul for precision craftsmanship. We do not create furniture, we place \"visual anchors\" in  space, forcing passers-by to stop and rethink the boundaries between life and objects the moment they meet the \"object\". Luanda Muck: In precise doubt, An",
